  <name>Headlamp</name>
  <summary>An easy-to-use and extensible web UI for Kubernetes</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Headlamp is an easy-to-use and extensible Kubernetes web UI.
      It was created to be a Kubernetes web UI that has the traditional
      functionality of other web UIs/dashboards available (i.e. to list and view
      resources) and extra functionality provided by plugins.
    </p>
  </description>
